      <title>独家：欧洲央行将维持市场利率下限但关注需求</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ecb-keep-floor-under-market-rates-with-eye-demand-sources-2024-02-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[四位消息人士告诉路透社，欧洲央行将在未来几年继续对市场利率设置“下限”，但银行将在决定所需流动性方面发挥更大作用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ecb-keep-floor-under-market-rates-with-eye-demand-sources-2024-02-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Feb 2024 06:03:51 GMT</pubDate>
